data.description: This is your opportunity to own a Spacious home in the growing community of Rainbow Lakes Estates. Located near Rainbow Springs and everything Central Florida has to offer. 3 Bedrooms and 3 Bathrooms with an over-sized lot! This home has many extras such as a Large In-Law Suite, a Wonderful Screened in Porch, and a Shed and Carport. Also, no worries with a Newer Roof and Newer HVAC System. You don't want to miss this one. Schedule your showing today!
